title: At The Center Pt. 1 ~ Bobby Hutcherson on where music goes
description:
In this SFJAZZ interview, vibraphone legend Bobby Hutcherson talks about where music goes when it's all said and done. Check out more video shorts with the NEA Jazz Master, former SFJAZZ Collective member and long-time San Francisco native!

For more videos, subscribe today to the SFJAZZ YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/SFJAZZOnline

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/SFJAZZ
Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/sfjazz

***SFJAZZ is a non-profit organization that presents year round jazz concerts, festivals and educational programs at the SFJAZZ Center in San Francisco, CA.
